### SCENARIO 7 — CUSTOMS AGENT: Export Documentation (Leila)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### S7.1 — Request Export Document (Fatima)
# @name createExportDoc
POST {{baseUrl}}/export-documents
Authorization: Bearer {{fatimaToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "certificationId": "{{certId}}",
  "destinationCountry": "DE",
  "hsCode": "09102000",
  "quantityKg": 10,
  "consigneeName": "Gewürzhaus GmbH",
  "consigneeCountry": "DE"
}

@exportDocId = {{createExportDoc.response.body.$.id}}

###

### S7.2 — Leila Reviews Pending Documents
GET {{baseUrl}}/export-documents?status=draft
Authorization: Bearer {{leilaToken}}

###

### S7.3 — View Export Document Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/export-documents/{{exportDocId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{leilaToken}}

###

### S7.4 — Validate Export Clearance
POST {{baseUrl}}/export-documents/{{exportDocId}}/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{leilaToken}}

###

### S7.5 — Download Export Certificate PDF
GET {{baseUrl}}/export-documents/{{exportDocId}}/certificate.pdf
Authorization: Bearer {{leilaToken}}

###

### S7.6 — View HS Codes
GET {{baseUrl}}/export-documents/hs-codes
Authorization: Bearer {{leilaToken}}

###

### S7.7 — Export Clearances Report CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/export-documents/clearances-report?from=2025-11-01&to=2025-11-30&destinationCountry=DE
Authorization: Bearer {{leilaToken}}


